      "span_text": "The systemic induction of detoxification by tissue-specific translation defects was not limited to the germline: tissue-specific translation deficits induced by RNAi in only muscle, neurons and hypodermis, using tissue-specific rescue of an rde-1 RNAi-defective mutant, can also induce a systemic detoxification in the intestine, showing that many cell types may be monitored by this system ( Supplementary Fig. 1i,j)."
